      "review_summary": "The PR adds bounded candidate-line diagnostics to edit-tool mismatch errors, with tests for indentation, escaping, indexed multi-edit failures, and no-op guard behavior.\n\nPR surface: Source +195, Tests +161. Total +356 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main is source-reproducible as lacking candidate-line diagnostics, and PR head source shows the remaining no-newline scan-bound issue in collectNormalizedLines.",
